    "componentChunkName": "component---src-templates-blog-template-js",
    "path": "/Redux/0105/",
    "result": {"data":{"cur":{"id":"487f3b6c-6a09-5c03-befa-07b70292a705","html":"<h1 id=\"redux\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#redux\" aria-label=\"redux permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Redux</h1>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">state</code>를 관리하는 도구<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">store</code>라는 저장소에서 component들의 state를 관리한다.<br>\ncomponent가 많아지고 관리해야하는 state가 많아지면 props drilling 문제가 발생한다.<br>\nredux를 사용하게 되면 모든 component에서 <code class=\"language-text\">reducer함수</code>와 <code class=\"language-text\">action</code>을 통해 state에 접근할 수 있다.\n<br/></p>\n<h1 id=\"redux로-state-관리하는-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#redux%EB%A1%9C-state-%EA%B4%80%EB%A6%AC%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"redux로 state 관리하는 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Redux로 state 관리하는 방법</h1>\n<p>action을 dispatch하면 reducer함수를 호출한다.<br>\nreducer는 store에 가서 현재 state값을 가져와 새로운 state 객체를 만들고 기존에 존재하던 default state 객체를 <code class=\"language-text\">대체</code>한다</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.888888888888886%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"redux1.png\"\n        title=\"redux1.png\"\n        src=\"/static/2c2083ddb0acdc3aed9b72262d80dda0/37523/redux1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2c2083ddb0acdc3aed9b72262d80dda0/e9ff0/redux1.png 180w,\n/static/2c2083ddb0acdc3aed9b72262d80dda0/f21e7/redux1.png 360w,\n/static/2c2083ddb0acdc3aed9b72262d80dda0/37523/redux1.png 720w,\n/static/2c2083ddb0acdc3aed9b72262d80dda0/302a4/redux1.png 1080w,\n/static/2c2083ddb0acdc3aed9b72262d80dda0/07a9c/redux1.png 1440w,\n/static/2c2083ddb0acdc3aed9b72262d80dda0/cea38/redux1.png 1644w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<br/>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.77777777777777%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"redux2.png\"\n        title=\"redux2.png\"\n        src=\"/static/b7faa7a01ea56680f718b874ae05a8a7/37523/redux2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b7faa7a01ea56680f718b874ae05a8a7/e9ff0/redux2.png 180w,\n/static/b7faa7a01ea56680f718b874ae05a8a7/f21e7/redux2.png 360w,\n/static/b7faa7a01ea56680f718b874ae05a8a7/37523/redux2.png 720w,\n/static/b7faa7a01ea56680f718b874ae05a8a7/302a4/redux2.png 1080w,\n/static/b7faa7a01ea56680f718b874ae05a8a7/07a9c/redux2.png 1440w,\n/static/b7faa7a01ea56680f718b874ae05a8a7/09b15/redux2.png 1704w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"state\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#state\" aria-label=\"state permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>state</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>기본 객체</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"action\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#action\" aria-label=\"action permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>action</h2>\n<p>기본값인 state를 바꾸는것\ndispatch로 action을 객체에 <code class=\"language-text\">전달</code>한다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">dispatch({type:TEST});\n\n//data 추가\ndispatch({type:TEST, data:'test'})</code></pre></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"dispatch\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dispatch\" aria-label=\"dispatch permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>dispatch</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>이전 action으로 돌아갈 수 있는 타임머신 기능과 어떤 동작이 취해졌는지에 대한 history가 제공되기 때문에 에러 핸들링이 쉬워진다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"reducer\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reducer\" aria-label=\"reducer permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reducer</h2>\n<p>action이 실행되면 Reducer에서 새로운 객체가 생성되고, 기존 store의 state 객체가 새로운 객체로 <code class=\"language-text\">대체</code>된다.\naction을 받아서 새로운 state를 만들어주는 역할\ndispatch된 액션이 reducer에 걸리고, 다음 state를 만들어낸다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">export const TEST = 'TEST';\n\nconst rootReducer = (state=0,action){\n switch(action.type){\n    case TEST\n    return state+1\n    dafult:\n    return state\n }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p>action을 dispatch하면 reducer함수가 호출이되는데<br>\ndispatch로 전달된 action.type에 따라 실행할 코드를 작성하면<br>\n이전 state에서 변경된 state를 확인하여\n<code class=\"language-text\">새로운 state 객체</code>를 반환해준다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"store\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#store\" aria-label=\"store permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Store</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import {createStore} from 'redux';\nexport const TEST = 'TEST';\n\nconst rootReducer = (state=0,action){\n switch(action.type){\n   case TEST\n     return state+1\n   dafult:\n    return state\n }\n}\n\nconst store = redux.createStore( rootReducer );//store 생성\nconsole.log(store.getState())//0 (현재 state 가져오기)\n\nstore.dispath({type:TEST})\nconsole.log(store.getState())//1</code></pre></div>\n<p>createStore로 store를 만들고</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>reducer에서 새로운 state값 반환하면<br>\nstore에 저장되어 있는 현재 state값이 업데이트된다.\n<br/>\n<br/>\nstore는 state를 관리해주고<br>\ngetState()는 메서드로 현재 state를 가져오며<br>\ndispatch를 통해 state를 업데이트할 수 있다.<br>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n그리고 store가 변경되면 dispatch가 store의 subscribe메서드를 통해<br>\n변경된 state값으로 다시 render해주게 된다.<br>\n그러면 변경된 ui로 stater값이 바뀌게된다.</p>","excerpt":"Redux 를 관리하는 도구 라는 저장소에서 component들의 state를 관리한다. component가 많아지고 관리해야하는 state가 많아지면 props drilling 문제가 발생한다. redux를 사용하게 되면 모든 component에서 와 을 통해 state에 접근할 수 있다.\n Redux로 state 관리하는 방법 action을 dispatch하면 reducer함수를 호출한다. reducer는 store에 가서 현재 state값을 가져와 새로운 state 객체를 만들고 기존에 존재하던 default state 객체를 한다 \n\n state 기본 객체 action 기본값인 state를 바꾸는것\ndispatch로 action을 객체에 한다. dispatch 이전 action으로 돌아갈 수 있는 타임머신 기능과 어떤 동작이 취해졌는지에 대한 history가 제공되기 때문에 에러 핸들링이 쉬워진다. Reducer action이 실행되면 Reducer에서 새로운 객체가 생성되…","frontmatter":{"date":"January 05, 2023","title":"Redux","categories":"Redux","author":"권형석","emoji":"📚"},"fields":{"slug":"/Redux/0105/"}},"next":{"id":"922fac00-2a47-5d4f-8856-6a45fa9847b0","html":"<blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"-에러상황\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%97%90%EB%9F%AC%EC%83%81%ED%99%A9\" aria-label=\" 에러상황 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>👨‍💻 에러상황</h1>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 719px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"blog01.png\"\n        title=\"blog01.png\"\n        src=\"/static/fa0b82c80843bab4177a00e783f0d002/073e9/blog01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fa0b82c80843bab4177a00e783f0d002/e9ff0/blog01.png 180w,\n/static/fa0b82c80843bab4177a00e783f0d002/f21e7/blog01.png 360w,\n/static/fa0b82c80843bab4177a00e783f0d002/073e9/blog01.png 719w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 719px) 100vw, 719px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<br/>\n<blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"-어떤-에러인가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%96%B4%EB%96%A4-%EC%97%90%EB%9F%AC%EC%9D%B8%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\" 어떤 에러인가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📚 어떤 에러인가?</h1>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">리액트 무한루프 렌더링</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>저장할 값을 setState에 넣을때 무한루프가 걸렸다.<br/>\n에러가 발생하는 원인은 렌더 과정에서 state를 변화하는 함수가 있다면 리랜더링이 계속 일어나면서 발생하는 에러임을 확인했다.<br/>\n(setState는 콜백으로 다시 렌더링을 트리거한다.)<br/>\nsetState는 비동기 방식으로 콜백큐가 모두 비워진 이후에 최종적으로 실행된다.<br/>\n아마 state의 계속된 변경으로 이러한 에러가 발생된듯하다.</p>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"에러-핸들링-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%97%90%EB%9F%AC-%ED%95%B8%EB%93%A4%EB%A7%81-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"에러 핸들링 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>에러 핸들링 방법</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">useEffect를 이용</code>하고 sideEffect로부터 보호하기.<br/>\nuseEffect <code class=\"language-text\">내부</code>에서 setState 로직을 넣어줬더니 문제 해결.<br/>\n의존성 배열을 빈배열로 놓았기 때문에 컴포넌트가 처음에 마운팅되고 난 이후에 로직실행.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">useEffect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">=></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token function\">setMyData</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n</blockquote>\n<br/>\n<blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"컴포넌트가-리렌더링-되는-조건은\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%BB%B4%ED%8F%AC%EB%84%8C%ED%8A%B8%EA%B0%80-%EB%A6%AC%EB%A0%8C%EB%8D%94%EB%A7%81-%EB%90%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4%EC%9D%80\" aria-label=\"컴포넌트가 리렌더링 되는 조건은 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>💡컴포넌트가 리렌더링 되는 조건은…</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">state</code>가 변경되었을때<br/>\n<code class=\"language-text\">부모컴포넌트</code>가 변경되었을때<br/>\n<code class=\"language-text\">props</code>가 변경되었을때</p>\n</blockquote>\n<br/>\n<blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"-추가로-알게된점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80%EB%A1%9C-%EC%95%8C%EA%B2%8C%EB%90%9C%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\" 추가로 알게된점 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>💡 추가로 알게된점</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">버튼 태그</code> 부분에서</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">const Counter = () => {\n   const [value, setValue] = useState(0);\n   return(\n       &lt;div>\n           &lt;div>{value}&lt;/div>\n           &lt;button onClick={setValue(prev => prev+1)}>+1&lt;/button>\n           &lt;button onClick={setValue(prev => prev-1)}>-1&lt;/button>\n       &lt;/div>\n   )\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Arrow function 방식</code>으로 state를 변경해야 에러가 발생하지 않는다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;button onClick={()=>setValue(prev=>prev+1)}>+1&lt;/button></code></pre></div>\n</blockquote>","frontmatter":{"date":"January 04, 2023","title":"Too many re-renders (SetState 관련 에러)","categories":"Error","author":"권형석","emoji":"😃"},"fields":{"slug":"/TIL/0104/"}},"prev":{"id":"121c263f-a39f-59c5-9098-fc7f6527866e","html":"<h4 id=\"기존에-사용했던-recoil-이외의-전역상태관리-라이브러리인-redux를-학습하며-정리합니다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%EC%A1%B4%EC%97%90-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%96%88%EB%8D%98-recoil-%EC%9D%B4%EC%99%B8%EC%9D%98-%EC%A0%84%EC%97%AD%EC%83%81%ED%83%9C%EA%B4%80%EB%A6%AC-%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%8C%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC%EC%9D%B8-redux%EB%A5%BC-%ED%95%99%EC%8A%B5%ED%95%98%EB%A9%B0-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC%ED%95%A9%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"기존에 사용했던 recoil 이외의 전역상태관리 라이브러리인 redux를 학습하며 정리합니다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>기존에 사용했던 recoil 이외의 전역상태관리 라이브러리인 redux를 학습하며 정리합니다.</h4>\n<h1 id=\"useselector\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#useselector\" aria-label=\"useselector permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>useSelector()</h1>\n<p>useSelector는 Redux store로부터 state를 가져올 때 사용한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import {createStore} from \"redux\";\n\nconst store = createStore(reducer);\n\nexport default store;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"usedispatch\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#usedispatch\" aria-label=\"usedispatch permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>useDispatch()</h1>\n<p>useDispatch는 action을 reducer로 dispatch할 때 사용할 수 있는 훅이다. (reducer로 dispatch하여 기존의 state를 <code class=\"language-text\">대체</code>한다)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import {useDispatch} from \"react-redux\"\n\nconst dispatch = useDispatch();\n\ndispatch(ACTION)</code></pre></div>\n<hr/>\n<h3 id=\"리덕스-작업을-위해서는-3개의-파일을-생성해야-한다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A6%AC%EB%8D%95%EC%8A%A4-%EC%9E%91%EC%97%85%EC%9D%84-%EC%9C%84%ED%95%B4%EC%84%9C%EB%8A%94-3%EA%B0%9C%EC%9D%98-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC%EC%9D%84-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%ED%95%B4%EC%95%BC-%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"리덕스 작업을 위해서는 3개의 파일을 생성해야 한다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>리덕스 작업을 위해서는 3개의 파일을 생성해야 한다.</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<li/>action   \n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>action을 생성하고, 해당 action이 어떤 일을 수행할지 지정한다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<li/>reducer   \n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>dispatch된 action을 실행시킬 reducer\naction 객체를 받아 기존의 state를 대체시킨다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<li/>store   \n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>reducer로 <code class=\"language-text\">global store</code>를 만든다</p>\n</blockquote>\n<br/>\n<h4 id=\"간단한-todo-list를-만들기-위해-todo를-추가하고-삭제하는-action을-만든다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%84%EB%8B%A8%ED%95%9C-todo-list%EB%A5%BC-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0-%EC%9C%84%ED%95%B4-todo%EB%A5%BC-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80%ED%95%98%EA%B3%A0-%EC%82%AD%EC%A0%9C%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-action%EC%9D%84-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A0%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"간단한 todo list를 만들기 위해 todo를 추가하고 삭제하는 action을 만든다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>간단한 todo-list를 만들기 위해 todo를 추가하고 삭제하는 action을 만든다.</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">export const add_todo = (todo) => {\n    return {\n        type:ADD,\n        todo:{\n            id: id++,\n            title: todo.title,\n            isComplete: todo.isComplete,\n        }\n    }\n};\n\nexport const delete_todo = (id) => {\n    return {\n        type: DELETE,\n        id,\n    }\n};</code></pre></div>\n<p>todo를 추가하기위해 매개변수로 받은 todo 객체를 reducer에게 반환하고, todo를 삭제하기 위해서는 삭제하려는 todo의 id만을 넘겨준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">const initialState = {\n    todos:[],\n};\n\n// action을 받아서 새로운 객체를 형성하고, store의 객체를 대체한다\nexport const reducers = (state = initialState, action) => {\n    if (action.type === ADD){\n        return{\n            todos:[...state.todos, action.todo],\n        };\n    }\n    \n    if (action.type === DELETE) {\n        return {\n            todos:[...state.todos.filter((todo) => todo.id !== action.id)]\n        }\n    }\n\n}</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">[ADD]</code>initialState로 todos라는 빈 배열을 만들고, 이 배열에 새로운 항목을 추가한 <code class=\"language-text\">새로운 state</code>를 반환하도록 한다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">[DELETE]</code>action이 넘겨줄 id를 가지고 <code class=\"language-text\">Array.filter()</code> 메서드를 이용해 id가 동일한 todo 객체를 삭제한 todos를 반환하도록 한다.`</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"store\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#store\" aria-label=\"store permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>store</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import {createStore} from \"redux\";\n\nconst store = createStore(reducer);\n\nexport default store;</code></pre></div>\n<p>리덕스 store에 reducer를 넣어주는 작업을 해당 파일에서 수행한다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"inputform\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#inputform\" aria-label=\"inputform permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>InputForm</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">export default function InputForm() {\n\n    const dispatch = useDispatch();\n    const [text, setText] = useState(\"\");\n\n    const handleChange = (e: any) => {\n        const {value} = e.target;\n        setText(value);\n        // console.log(\"text\", text)\n    };\n\n    const handleClick = () => {\n        if (text.trim() === ''){\n            alert(\"글자를 입력해주세요\");\n            return;\n        };\n        const todo = {\n            title: text,\n            isComplete:false,\n        }\n        // action을 dispatch\n        dispatch(add_todo(todo));\n        alert(\"입력되었습니다\");\n        setText(\"\");\n\n    };\n\n    const handleKeyPress = (e:any) => {\n        if(e.key === \"Enter\"){\n            handleClick();\n        }\n    };\n\n\n  return (\n    &lt;Wrapper>\n        &lt;Input placeholder='Write down your todos' onChange={handleChange} onKeyDown={handleKeyPress}/>\n        &lt;Buttons onClick={handleClick}>Add&lt;/Buttons>\n    &lt;/Wrapper>\n  )\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"todoitem\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#todoitem\" aria-label=\"todoitem permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>todoItem</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">export default function TodoItem({todo}) {\n    const dispatch = useDispatch();\n\n    const {id, title, isComplete} = todo;\n\n\n\n    // action(delete_todo)을 dispatch한다.\n    const handleClick = () => {\n        dispatch(delete_todo(id))\n    }\n  return (\n    &lt;Wrapper>\n      &lt;input type=\"checkbox\" onClick={handleCheck}/>\n        &lt;Title>{title}&lt;/Title>\n        {/* &lt;div onClick={handleClick}>x&lt;/div> */}\n        &lt;IconWrapper>\n          &lt;BsPen style={{cursor:'pointer', marginRight:'20px'}}/>\n          &lt;BsTrash onClick={handleClick} style={{cursor:'pointer'}}/>\n        &lt;/IconWrapper>\n    &lt;/Wrapper>\n  )\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p>여기에서는 todo item을 삭제, 즉 해당 todo를 완료했을 경우를 위해 DELETE ACTION을 dispatch한다. 이를 위해 useDispatch()를 사용했다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"todolist\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#todolist\" aria-label=\"todolist permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>todoList</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">export default function TodoList() {\n    const todos = useSelector((state:any) => state?.todos);\n\n  return (\n        &lt;Wrapper>\n          {todos?.map((todo:any) => (\n              &lt;TodoItem key={todo.id} todo={todo}>&lt;/TodoItem>\n          ))}\n         &lt;/Wrapper>\n    \n  )\n}</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"date":"January 10, 2023","title":"Redux","categories":"Redux","author":"권형석","emoji":"📚"},"fields":{"slug":"/Redux/0110/"}},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://hskwon5170.github.io","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":""}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Redux/0105/","nextSlug":"/TIL/0104/","prevSlug":"/Redux/0110/"}},
    "staticQueryHashes": ["1073350324","1956554647","2938748437"]}